00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:44.440
Mr. Gu, why haven't you
started the car yet?

00:10:44.960 --> 00:10:45.639
Miss Lu.

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:46.759
Actually,

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:48.639
